headline: 3 Dividend Stocks to Buy Now That Are Crushing the S&P 500 in 2025
summary: Home security specialist Allegion is a company with secure long-term growth prospects.  Pitney Bowes' cost-cutting has delivered results, and shareholders are benefiting.  The S&P 500 has rocketed higher in recent weeks but is still down year to date at the time of this writing.
